## Simultaneous/Structural Equations

Two equations:

$$
\begin{aligned}
\text{NGSE} & = \beta_1 \text{SOP} + e_1 \\
\text{PASS} & = \beta_2 \text{NGSE} + \beta_3 \text{SOP} + e_2
\end{aligned}
$$


